collection.name: FameLadySquad
collection.description:
Fame Lady Squad is the first ever all-female generative avatar collection on the Ethereum blockchain. Yes, we are *THE* community who took over a project to write our own story. This is NFT history. This is HERstory. 

FLS are 8888 distinctive Ladies made up of millions of fierce trait combinations.

Community = Everything. Commercial IP rights of each Lady NFT belong to its owner.
